item.content:encoded:
URL:

https://github.com/CryptoidCoder/Git-Template

About:

A template project repository with everything needed for a git project on it. (How To Setup git Stuff)

Branches:

main – Has Everything On It

Setup:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run:

./venv/Scripts/python.exe main.py

Designed For Use With The Procfile In Heroku
